body:
I just recently got into yokai watch and honestly I’ve been missing out on so much
I was one of those people you didn’t care for it because it was “just pokemon” but as a big pokemon I fell in love with it because of that and it has its own nice charm
So honestly why do pokemon fans say that they don’t like yokai watch??? Because it’s like pokemon??? Bitch if you like pokemon then what’s the problem????
